Fix broken League of Legends on Linux with a friend and without download whole game
From friend comptuer : compress the game folder to zip (or tar for linux)
On your computer :
Install Lutris flatpak, download and set « wine GE lol » to default wine.
Download the official setup.exe to install LOL
Use Lutris to run LOL setup.exe and wait on the splash screen ready to install.
Extract game compressed in the folder game ready to install.
Back on the splash screen ready to install LOL and click on Install, it will check and repair the game.
With Lutris, create a new installed game from file, then select the LeagueoflegendsClient.exe from the game folder and set the « wine GE lol » to use.
